the farmers almanac renewing its crusade 
to revamp the nations coinage and currency is promoting a 1 coin 
to replace the dollar bill to pinch a few pennies for uncle sam and 
taxpayers 
the almanacs 1990 edition just off the presses also calls for 
the elimination of the penny and 50cent piece the new 1 coin 
