the feeling of national dignity was constantly being crushed in 
our country he said through an interpreter if they even wanted 
to build a school they had to go hat in hand so to speak to 
moscow it was very offensive 
giving soviet republics more power to govern themselves would 
greatly reduce tensions he said 
the problem is serious enough he said that he was cutting his 
twoweek tour by a week to attend a special meeting in moscow to 
discuss the nationalities issue if the problem is to be solved the 
ruling politburo must be reinvigorated with progressivethinking 
leaders yeltsin said 
we have so many odious and incompetent people in the 
politburo he said all they do is raise questions and never 
answer them they are hanging on to their positions with dear life 
we need to catapult them out like they do with ejection seats but 
