students returning to class this fall are returning home if their 
hairs too long or skirts too short as more high schools across 
the country enact new hair and dress codes to impose official ideas 
of fashion 
but some parents and students say theres too much ado about 
hairdos and the clothes kids wear they argue that long hair or 
