several texas school systems have new dress codes mostly aimed 
at offensive or suggestive tshirts and baltimore schools banned 
furs costly jewelry and leather coats dozens of other systems 
including some in michigan new york and louisiana adopted 
voluntary dress codes for schools to consider 
