he said at the time he did not consider it a discussion of 
the case and to this day does not 
the house voting unanimously for impeachment alleged 
nixon lied when he told a grand jury he never discussed the case 
against drew fairchild with holmes 
nixon lied when he told a grand jury he had nothing to do 
