foreign relations committee called gregg a man of integrity and 
honesty and said his detractors see in him a good way to bash 
george bush 
i think it is fair to say that mr gregg was masterful in 
refuting the major allegations against him helms said 
lets get george bush thats what this is all about get 
george bush tear him down helms said 
