austerity and that he has inherited about 7 million dollars of 
debt and an operating deficit that now exceeds 1 million which he 
cites as evidence of past mismanagement 
other tribal leaders maintain that there was an operating surplus 
when mitchell took over and that outside audits of tribal finances 
