here is a synopsis of the six felony counts to which the 
investment giant drexel burnham lambert inc pleaded guilty monday 
1 securities fraud for the fraudulent filing of required 
disclosure documents known as schedule 13ds in connection with the 
pennsylvania engineering corp takeover of fischbach corp 
2 mail fraud for the manipulation of mca inc common stock 
during golden nugget incs sale of its mca holdings 
3 securities fraud for unlawfully aiding disgraced stock 
